snippet.title: Battle Fleet Ground Assault - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/400350/Battle_Fleet_Ground_Assault/

Battle Fleet: Ground Assault takes some of the most exciting tank theaters of war from WWII and puts them on your desktop in this action packed turn-based strategy game. Battle Fleet: Ground Assault boasts a wide array of historically accurate WWII vehicles and tanks as well as different play environments that provide topographical challenges during combat. 

Find out more at:
http://www.battlefleetgame.com/ground-assault.html
